des:
Reno Market Updates brings you weekly information in the Real Estate Market for Reno, Sparks, and the surrounding areas. 

Add this to your Flash Briefing to stay up to date on local market movements, including price information and homes listed and sold.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
